  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Cristo wajyashan runasta:
 "Kunanjampuway," nispa./
 /Uyarispa, usqhayllata qhatíkusunchej,
 Kasuspa Palabranta./
 
[V2]
 /Jesucristo Diospa Churin
 Runasman sufinchashan./
 /"Pichus Noqaman jamonqa, chay runaspajpis
 Salvacionqa wakisqa/V
 
[V3]
 /Kunampachataj qowasun
 Allin kusiy sonqota./
 /Kamachisqanman jinata kawsayninchejpi
 Kunan purina tíyan./
 
</lyrics></song>